Rosie Mac https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rosie_Mac 0 Rosie Mac (born 12 February 1997) is an actress, model and singer from England. She was the body double for Emilia Clarke in her portrayal of Daenerys Targaryen in season five of the HBO series Game of Thrones.
